# collar — wsl

> Windows Subsystem for Linux path translation. Mount points, drive mapping.

---

### Entity: wsl

Host→ Windows:below(11) | FS:mountmnt(11) | Drive:Cslash(11)
Path→ User:Users(11) | Desktop:mntc(11) | Translate:equiv(11)

```yaml
entity: wsl
type: entity
properties:
  id:
    type: string
    required: true
    default: wsl
states: [active]
lifecycle: active
```